Global Active Vibration Control System Market Insights
Active Vibration Control System Market size was valued at USD 2.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 4.0 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Active Vibration Control System Market Overview
The Active Vibration Control System market is expected to grow significantly in the coming years, driven by advancements in technologies and increasing demand across industries such as aerospace, automotive, and industrial machinery. The market size is valued at approximately USD 2.5 billion in 2024 and is projected to expand at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 7.5%, reaching USD 4.2 billion by 2030. This growth is primarily driven by the rising need for noise and vibration control in high-performance applications. The system’s ability to provide real-time adjustment to vibration disturbances ensures enhanced durability and operational efficiency across various applications.

